rchase at UN dining facilities, including Riverview Cafeteria, Lobby Caf=C3=
=A9, Vienna Caf=C3=A9, and Visitors Caf=C3=A9. Hours may vary. See the <a h=
ref=3D"https://ggim.un.org/meetings/GGIM-committee/14th-Session/documents/U=
